{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "With the two gendarme, the policemen, came some of the local so-called big shots to witness that-- what going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some of these three man who came with the gendarme, these were all friends of my father, that he served together in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In a way, they were so ashamed that they had to witness and they have to be there, so they were all sitting front of the house in one of this frame and talking and smoking and all that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The meantime, the-- the gendarme came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Czigler-- Czigler [NON-ENGLISH], because that was the title in Europe, I want to see your family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we lined up like an organ key.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he looked at us and we had our little earrings in our ear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Meantime, when we know that they are coming, my mother suggested that we should hide some of the jewelry, so my mother said, I'm going to give my diamond ring and my brother with the watch, because in Europe, that was the custom.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When a boy got bar mitzvahed, they got a beautiful gold pocket watch with a gold chain, so my father had it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So when my mother said that, let's take the watch from Philip, and I will gave my rings and the bracelet and all the other thing-- so my father said, no, because they know that every Jewish woman have a diamond ring, and also every boy has a watch.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But all the other jewelry that we had, like extra rings and things like that-- so my brother and myself we went up to the attic.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And as you know, we had like these beams that holds the roof, so we put it in one of the joint.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
